      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is a bit long. Also, in resultdb\u0027s proto definition, this is called test status rather than result status.\n\nWe can rename it to\n1. TEST-STATUS, but it\u0027s actually filtering the results.\n2. STATUS, but users may confuse this with variant status.",
